column5: coming soon...   got our first fish of the season tonite... no so lucky for the fish!!        and I've come to realize.. im no carpenter.. nor can I paint worth a crap.  and finally UFC on the big screen!!    and were done the porch,  too bad theres still no bugs up here... lol
I'm jealous! Cant wait for the UFC tonight, my bro's in Vegas watching it from the 3rd row, I'm jealous of him too.  Jealousy is taking me over
I forgot UFC was on,  I had better preorder it , now  nice set up at the camp, can it get any better
I just happen to know an ol' retnek Master Carpenter that will work on a per diem basis... PM me if you have several thousand dollars to blow in labor!  The camp is really looking good!!!
How about $20, and all the shine ya can drink!!
I might come up and watch you work for that amount!
You must be real proud of your accomplishments TJ!!!!  Great looking bass by the way Leechman
Thanks for the reminder Terry! Enjoy the fish n Fight  Boys!! Go Rahshad!!
a couple of really good fights, Rahshad who wasn't he a good fighter at one time...LOL
I don't want to know why there is a litre of oil in the bedroom. Jim
i don't know where you are but is bass season not closed there?
Oh no and He took pictures of them.....
Congrats on the bass T.J.  the set up in the cabin is impressive...very cool.
Bass is open year round in my area.
Sweet!!!  Looking good TJ.  I can taste that bass right now (or wish I could   )  Camp is looking very inviting my friend  Joey
Very, Very INVITING if you ask me.......
